        <heading>3288.  Requirements of contract of mortgage</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 3288.  Requirements of contract of mortgage
A contract of mortgage must state precisely the nature and situation of each of the immovables or other property over which it is granted; state the amount of the obligation, or the maximum amount of the obligations that may be outstanding at any time and from time to time that the mortgage secures; and be signed by the mortgagor.</p>
        </content>
